title: 2 Bedroom Luxury Home! Laundry, Garages, Pools, MORE
posting_body: ['Our luxury apartment homes feature spacious 1, 2, and 3+ bedroom apartment home in a variety of styles, floor plans, and layouts; as well as, vaulted ceilings in select homes, updated color schemes, and wonderful staff with top-notch customer service.', 'At Kingston Green Estates, amenities are very important to us.', 'Our amenities include:', '- Heated Indoor and Outdoor Pools', '- Whirlpool/Spa', '- Sauna', '- Fitness Room', '- Community Room', '- Underground Parking', '- Elevators in each building', '- 24hr Emergency Maintenance', '- Management On-Site and So Much More!', 'Each apartment home is furnished with appliances which include the following: Refrigerator, Oven/Stove, Microwave, Dishwasher, and In-Home Laundry with Washer and Dryer.', 'Call today and set up a time to view your new home', 'show contact info', ") or stop by whenever you're ready!", 'HOURS: Monday through Friday (9:00am - 6:00pm) and Saturday (11:00am - 4:00pm).', 'Visit us online at <URL> for additional details on our homes and prices!', 'We hope to be the next place you can call home!']
